I"f<p>By default, <strong>VCSA</strong> still asks for a login password, even if you set up a SSH pubkey properly in the <code class="highlighter-rouge">authorized_keys</code> file.
To get rid of the password prompt, just change the default shell to <em>bash</em>:</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>chsh <span class="nt">-s</span> /bin/bash
</code></pre></div></div>

